---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ImageConverter from '../../components/ImageConverter.jsx';
import RelatedTools from '../../components/RelatedTools.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Convert Image Online Free – PNG to JPG, JPG to PNG"
  description="Convert PNG to JPG, JPG to PNG, or WebP to JPG instantly online for free. No upload to servers, no login. Fast browser-based image format converter."
>
  <div class="tool-page">
    <div class="tool-header">
      <a href="/categories/image-tools/" class="back-link">← Image Tools</a>
      <h1 class="tool-title">Image Converter</h1>
      <p class="tool-subtitle">Convert between PNG, JPG and WebP formats in one click. Free, instant, completely private.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ad-slot ad-slot-horizontal">
      <ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX" data-ad-slot="1234567890" data-ad-format="auto" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
      <script is:inline>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script>
    </div>

    <ImageConverter client:load />

    <div class="ad-slot ad-slot-horizontal" style="margin-top: 32px;">
      <ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX" data-ad-slot="0987654321" data-ad-format="auto" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
      <script is:inline>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script>
    </div>

    <section class="seo-content">
      <h2>How to convert an image format online</h2>
      <p>Select your desired conversion direction (e.g. PNG to JPG), upload your image, and click Convert. Your converted file downloads instantly. No account, no waiting, no file size limits imposed by the browser.</p>

      <h2>PNG to JPG — when and why</h2>
      <p>JPG is a lossy compressed format optimized for photographs. Converting a PNG to JPG typically reduces file size by 50–80%, making images much faster to load on websites and easier to share. The trade-off is that JPG does not support transparency. If your PNG has a transparent background, the converted JPG will replace it with white.</p>

      <h2>JPG to PNG — when and why</h2>
      <p>PNG uses lossless compression and supports transparent backgrounds, making it ideal for logos, icons, graphics and screenshots. Converting JPG to PNG won't recover lost quality (JPG is lossy), but it gives you a lossless container for further editing without adding more compression artifacts.</p>

      <h2>WebP — what is it and should I convert?</h2>
      <p>WebP is Google's modern image format designed for the web. It achieves roughly 25–35% smaller file sizes than JPG at equivalent quality. However, WebP isn't universally supported by older software and some platforms still require JPG. Convert WebP to JPG when you need maximum compatibility.</p>

      <h2>Is my image safe?</h2>
      <p>Your image never leaves your device. The conversion uses the browser's native Canvas API — no uploads, no servers, no third-party processing of any kind.</p>
    </section>

    <RelatedTools slugs={["compress-image", "webp-to-jpg", "resize-image"]} />
  </div>
</Layout>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebApplication",
  "name": "Image Converter",
  "url": "https://www.pixmidas.com/tools/convert-image/",
  "applicationCategory": "UtilitiesApplication",
  "operatingSystem": "Any",
  "browserRequirements": "Requires JavaScript",
  "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "0", "priceCurrency": "USD" },
  "description": "Convert PNG to JPG, JPG to PNG, or WebP to JPG online for free. Browser-based, no uploads, instant conversion."
}
</script>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How do I convert an image format online for free?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Select your desired conversion direction (e.g. PNG to JPG), upload your image, and click Convert. Your converted file downloads instantly. No account, no waiting." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "When should I convert PNG to JPG?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Convert PNG to JPG when you need to reduce file size by 50–80% for websites or sharing. Note that JPG does not support transparency — transparent PNG backgrounds will become white." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is WebP and should I convert it?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "WebP is Google's modern image format that achieves 25–35% smaller file sizes than JPG. Convert WebP to JPG when you need maximum compatibility with older software or platforms." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is my image safe when converting formats?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Your image never leaves your device. The conversion uses the browser's native Canvas API — no uploads, no servers, no third-party processing of any kind." }
    }
  ]
}
</script>
